Columns.Name: Chests
Columns.Description: Randomize chests that don't fit into the other categories.

Columns.Name: Npc Rewards
Columns.Description: Randomize items rewarded by NPCs except Minigames.

Columns.Name: Freestanding
Columns.Description: Randomize freestanding items.

Columns.Name: Purchases
Columns.Description: Randomize purchases including shops, scrubs, tingle, bean man, milk bar and Gorman Bros.

Columns.Name: Starting Items
Columns.Description: Randomize starting items.

Columns.Name: Minigames
Columns.Description: Randomize items rewarded from minigames.

Columns.Name: Boss Fights
Columns.Description: Randomize items earned by fighting bosses/minibosses.

Columns.Name: Moon Items
Columns.Description: Randomize items on The Moon.

Columns.Name: Enemy Spawn
Columns.Description: Randomize items spawned by enemies including freestanding Golden Skulltulas, enemies that normally spawn Stray Fairies and Takkuri.

Columns.Name: Grass
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed dropped from grass. Only Keaton Grass and grass such as that near owl statues drop fixed items.

Columns.Name: Jars
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from jars including small jars and green jars.

Columns.Name: Crates
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from small and large crates.

Columns.Name: Small Snowballs
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from small snowballs.

Columns.Name: Large Snowballs
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from large snowballs.

Columns.Name: Barrels
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from barrels. This includes items that already exist within barrels before they're destroyed.

Columns.Name: Beehives
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from beehives.

Columns.Name: Invisible Items
Columns.Description: Randomize invisible items.

Columns.Name: Events
Columns.Description: Randomize items spawned by events including the Moon's Tear, the Sword School Gong, the Song Wall in Termina Field, the Telescope Guay and the Termina Field circling Guay.

Columns.Name: Soft Soil
Columns.Description: Randomize items from soft soil.

Columns.Name: Hit Spots
Columns.Description: Randomize items dropped by hitting specific spots in the game.

Columns.Name: Rocks
Columns.Description: Randomize fixed drops from rocks. Only rocks on walls drop fixed items. Also includes the item within the Red Rock in Mountain Village spring time.

Columns.Name: Scoops
Columns.Description: Randomize bottle scoops.

Columns.Name: Glitches Required
Columns.Description: Randomize items that require glitches to collect.

Rows.Name: Main Inventory
Rows.Description: Randomize items on the main inventory screen other than trade items. Also includes Bombers' Notebook, Swords, Mirror Shield and Wallets.

Rows.Name: Songs
Rows.Description: Randomize songs except Song of Soaring.

Rows.Name: Trade Items
Rows.Description: Randomize Moon's Tear, Title Deeds, Letter to Kafei, Pendant of Memories, Room Key and Letter to Mama.

Rows.Name: Navigation
Rows.Description: Randomize Dungeon Maps/Compasses and overworld maps.

Rows.Name: Magic Powers
Rows.Description: Randomize non-item Great Fairy rewards including Magic Power, Great Spin Attack, Extended Magic Power and Double Defense.

Rows.Name: Skulltula Tokens
Rows.Description: Randomize golden skulltula tokens. Tokens will not reset to 0 after Song of Time.

Rows.Name: Stray Fairies
Rows.Description: Randomize stray fairies including the Clock Town stray fairy. Stray fairies will not reset to 0 after Song of Time.

Rows.Name: Dungeon Keys
Rows.Description: Randomize small keys and boss keys.

Rows.Name: Recovery Hearts
Rows.Description: Randomize the recovery hearts in Pirates' Fortress.

Rows.Name: Magic Jars
Rows.Description: Randomize large and small magic jars.

Rows.Name: Chateau
Rows.Description: Randomize the Chateau refill. Bottle with Chateau Romani is part of Main Inventory

Rows.Name: Fairy
Rows.Description: Randomize the Fairy purchase in the Trading Post.

Rows.Name: Time Travel
Rows.Description: Randomize Ocarina and Song of Time.

Rows.Name: Royal Wallet
Rows.Description: Add the Royal Wallet to the item pool.
